{"tid":1578874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察婚禮","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T10:20:28.000Z","uid":201751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9821204e07c6102652b493d76718298bae00d3f","tid":1578874,"uid":201751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:13:43.000Z","msg":"其實如果警察結婚 喺咪可以去參加吓 唔去參加吓  睇吓抽唔抽得中佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好搞人地婚禮 一世人一次"},{"pid":"d09f7c7af057e16107d497b533695b8fb29e59d3","tid":1578874,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:14:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37709811210dc0c8482b32031b1afe47b81fb3db","tid":1578874,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EEt_hKMXYAIDATl?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEEt_hKMXYAIDATl%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=d4111daf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96a96c60a224679ed9270b0e366a7b2e239859c3","tid":1578874,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:07.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b384e9492cb606ceb4ec5825e550628e6bb36ff","tid":1578874,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f55ac073ea4ad446a5ca0fb5fb15f38095f0f33a","tid":1578874,"uid":264382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:16:34.000Z","msg":"手足小心<br />\n沿途好鬼異 好多兩三個人 係街停留 我諗係便衣 真係叫佢哋小心 相信唔少於10部警車係新蒲崗"},{"pid":"20b1a7f155baa708c35bd2572856a548638749d6","tid":1578874,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"1b43efc14a8dbbbb1100630239c243f7a2a917b8","tid":1578874,"uid":154212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"你又知一生人一次？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296241bd6e11b41c75e129f1c2f9dbad30514b79","tid":1578874,"uid":164368,"like":1,"dislik